FBIS4-18370 "drweu064_q_94014" FBIS-WEU-94-064 Daily Report 2 Apr 1994 TURKEY Finance Minister Says Capital Tax `Unthinkable' Finance Minister Says Capital Tax `Unthinkable' TA0304064494 Ankara TRT Television Network in Turkish 1700 GMT 2 Apr 94 TA0304064494 Ankara TRT Television Network Turkish BFN [Announcer-read report over still of Finance and Customs Minister Ismet Atilla] [Text] Finance and Customs Minister Ismet Atilla has repudiated claims that a net wealth or capital tax will be included in the stabilization program which is being prepared by the government. In a written statement, Atilla stated that including a net wealth or capital tax in the stabilization program prepared by the government is unthinkable.
